dc_title_s: Laurie and Whittle's new map of London, with its environs, 1809.10
dc_description_s: Designed to be folded to 20 x 12 cm. 1 map: hand col., dissected in 20 sections and mounted on linen; 56 x 77 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
